metadata.name: Fortune! Raffle No.1 TICKET
metadata.description: This Raffle Ticket is valid for Fortune! Raffle #1 and the prizes is a BAYC Apefest 2022 Stencil Hoodie (Size M).  After 100 tickets are sold, a Steezy Ape Gang NFT #3921 will be added to the prize pool for one lucky winner.  Good luck everyone!
